D9%2584%25D8%25AC%25D9%258A%25D8%25B4-%25D8%25A7%25D9%2584%25D8%25A3%25D9%2585%25D9%258A%25D8%25B1%25D9%2583%25D9%258A%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAl-Mamlaka%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20defensive%20line%2C%20which%20the%20Russians%20spent%20many%20months%20preparing%2C%20it's%20got%20minefields%2C%20it's%20got%20dragon's%20teeth%2C%20it's%20got%20tank%20ditches.%20It's%20a%20very%2C%20very%20complex%20set%20of%20defensive%20preparations%20that%20the%20Ukrainians%20are%20fighting%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20counteroffensive%20is%20%26quot%3Bslower%20than%20the%20planners%20had%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20Milley%20said%20this%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20war%20when%20lives%20are%20at%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20making%20steady%20progress%20of%20400-500%20meters%20or%20sometimes%20up%20to%201%2C000%20meters%20a%20day%2C%20Milley%20said%2C%20and%20has%20liberated%20a%20considerable%20portion%20of%20Russian-occupied%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20while%20it's%20too%20early%20to%20tell%20whether%20the%20counteroffensive%20has%20succeeded%20or%20failed%2C%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20it's%20had%20partial%20success.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20kicking%20out%20200%2C000%20or%20300%2C000%20Russian%20troops%20will%20be%20difficult%2C%20said%20the%20top%20US%20general%2C%20Ukraine%20still%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20amount%20of%20combat%20power%20remaining.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bastards%20are%20rapidly%20advancing%2C%20covered%20by%20artillery%20strikes%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukraine%20artillery%20M777%20howitzer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e9f1f2b413420019a3fd29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukraine%20soldier%20covers%20his%20ears%20as%20an%20M777%20howitzer%20is%20fired%20on%20the%20f