EThe%20ruling%20comes%20as%20union%20membership%20across%20the%20country%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flabor-union-membership-fell-lowest-rate-record-2022-2023-1%5C%22%3Eremain%20historically%20low%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20something%20that%20labor%20advocates%20attribute%20to%20weakening%20labor%20laws%20and%20anti-union%20tactics%20from%20employers.%20The%20new%20ruling%20might%20chip%20away%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20a%20fringe%20ruling%2C%20this%20is%20a%20big%20ruling%2C%26quot%3B%20Groshen%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20a%20deterrent%20to%20companies%20to%20use%20techniques%20that%20might%20be%20ruled%20illegal%20in%20the%20past%20during%20campaigns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-unionize-illegal-union-busting-nlrb-rules-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693052102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e8e908b413420019a3a203%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-unionize-illegal-union-busting-nlrb-rules-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20ruling%20from%20the%20NLRB%20puts%20in%20place%20tougher%20consequences%20if%20companies%20try%20to%20use%20illegal%20union-busting%20tactics%20to%20squash%20organizing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-unionize-illegal-union-busting-nlrb-rules-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20economic%20model%20isn't%20working%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20country's%20headed%20for%20a%20'Lehman%20moment'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22China's%20economy%20is%20facing%20a%20troubled%20property%20sector%2C%20deflation%2C%20and%20weak%20trade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e78be052bc2d0019916c0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEconomists%20are%20wary%20on%20China%2C%20but%20many%20don't%20expect%20a%20Lehman%20moment%20to%20transpire.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%20%2F%20Stringer%2C%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChina's%20economy%20hasn't%20rebounded%20from%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20its%20troubles%20have%20fueled%20talks%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BLehman%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChina%20experts%20and%20economists%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20troubles%20in%20the%20property%20sector%20are%20serious%2C%20but%20different%20from%20the%202008%20US%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20going%20to%20have%20a%20comparable%20banking%20crisis%20because%20of%20the%20simple%20reason%20you%20have%20a%20state-owned%20financial%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20chatter%20of%20China%20facing%20its%20own%20%26quot%3BLehman%20moment%26quot%3B%20hasn't%20emerged%20out%20of%20thin%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Xi%20Jinping%20is%20overseeing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-deflation-markets-property-real-estate-housing-beijing-2023-8%5C%22%3Enightmare%20cocktail%20of%20economic%20hurdles%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20include%20a%20huge%20pile%20of%20debt%2C%20an%20ailing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountry-garden-china-real-estate-problems-explainer-evergrande-2023-8%5C%22%3Eproperty%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20demographic%20hurdles%2C%20and%20deteriorating%20foreign%20investment%20and%20trade.%20And%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20crisis%20that%20ultimately%20toppled%20Lehman%20Brothers%20in%202008%2C%20much%20of%20China's%20troubles%20are%20rooted%20in%20its%20property%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20economists%20and%20policy%20experts%20say%20that%20risks%20are%20high%2C%20they%20also%20say%20the%20situation%20is%20unlikely%20to%20catalyze%20an%20event%20like%20the%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina's%20property%20crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFront%20and%20center%20for%20any%20comparison%20between%20today's%20China%20and%20the%20US%20in%202008%20is%20the%20real%20estate%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20the%20US%2C%20which%20both%20then%20and%20now%20counts%20property%20as%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20most%20people's%20wealth%2C%20real%20estate%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20come%20to%20account%20for%20roughly%2020%25%20of%20China's%20GDP.%20A%20survey%20by%20the%20People's%20Bank%20of%20China%20in%202020%20found%20that%20property%20accounted%20for%2059%25%20of%20household%20wealth%2C%20and%20three-quarters%20of%20household%20liabilities.%20That%20means%20consumer%20confidence%20%E2%80%94%20how%20people%20feel%20%E2%80%94%20is%20closely%20tied%20to%20the%20property%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlfredo%20Montufar-Helu%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20China%20Center%20at%20the%20Conference%20Board%2C%20told%20Insider%20he%20does%20not%20anticipate%20a%20Lehman%20moment%2C%20but%20he%20maintained%20that%20China's%20old%20economic%20model%20may%20have%20run%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20boom%20that%20characterized%20the%20property%20sector%20of%20the%20last%20decade%20is%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BChina%20is%20at%20a%20crucial%20moment%20where%20they%20cannot%20stop%20supporting%20the%20supply%20side%2C%20because%20economic%20growth%20would%20decelerate%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20they%20need%20reforms%20on%20the%20demand%20side.%20Hopefully%20the%20intentions%20alone%20can%20generate%20more%20confidence%20in%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Citi%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20an%20August%20note%20that%20default%20worries%20for%20firms%20like%20Zhongrong%20Trust%E2%80%94a%20troubled%20shadow%20bank%20with%20massive%20exposure%20to%20real%20estate%E2%80%94have%20escalated%20thanks%20to%20the%20downturn%20in%20the%20property%20sector%2C%20but%20they%2C%20too%2C%20don't%20see%20it%20as%20the%20start%20of%20a%20Lehman%20moment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20given%20the%20scale%20of%20China's%20property%20market%2C%20policymakers%20may%20need%20to%20step%20in%20with%20fiscal%20stimulus%20to%20avoid%20catastrophe.%20That%2C%20however%2C%20can%20make%20asset%20price%20bubbles%20bigger%20and%20drive%20up%20debt%2C%20according%20to%C2%A0William%20Hurst%2C%20deputy%20director%20for%20the%20Centre%20for%20Geopolitics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20think%20about%20the%202008%20collapse%20in%20the%20US%20property%20market%2C%20driven%20by%20excessive%20wealth%20plowed%20into%20real%20estate%2C%20versus%20what's%20happening%20in%20China%20with%20much%20higher%20amounts%20of%20wealth%20in%20that%20sector%2C%20the%20scale%20and%20severity%20of%20the%20crisis%20is%20potentially%20much%20much%20worse%20than%20what%20happened%2015%20years%20ago%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Hurst%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20most%20of%20Chinese%20households'%20debt%20is%20tied%20to%20mortgages%2C%20and%20it's%20climbed%20so%20fast%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20that%20it's%20hovering%20near%20levels%20seen%20in%20the%20US%20pre-Great%20Financial%20Crisis.%20But%20unlike%20in%202008%2C%20homeowners%20in%20China%20are%20paying%20off%20their%20debts%2C%20and%20the%20share%20of%20people%20fulfilling%20their%20obligations%20outpaces%20the%20number%20of%20foreclosures%2C%20Montufar-Helu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStimulus%20on%20the%20supply%20side%20%E2%80%94%20facilitating%20financing%2C%20decreasing%20taxes%2C%20reducing%20business%20costs%2C%20fiscal%20investment%20%E2%80%94%20all%20that%20is%20rapid%2C%20and%20has%20a%20short-term%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20China's%20demand-side%20imbalances%20are%20long-term%2C%20and%20it%20needs%20to%20transition%20from%20industrialization-led%20to%20consumption-led%20economic%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDifferent%20political%20economies%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDrawing%20parallels%20between%20market-driven%20economies%20like%20the%20US%20or%20Japan%20is%20misleading%2C%20as%20it%20detracts%20from%20the%20reality%20of%20China's%20government-regulated%2C%20capital-controlled%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20though%20that%20hasn't%20necessarily%20prevented%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-stocks-economy-hang-seng-bear-market-hong-kong-deflation-2023-8%5C%22%3Eglobal%20investors%20from%20becoming%20spooked%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20month%2C%20bleak%20economic%20figures%20have%20rolled%20out%20of%20China%20at%20a%20startling%20clip.%20Production%20data%2C%20retail%20sales%2C%20consumer%20prices%2C%20and%20exports%20are%20all%20trending%20lower%2C%20while%20major%20property%20developers%20like%20Country%20Garden%20Holdings%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fasia%2Fchinas-country-garden-missed-two-dollar-bond-coupon-payments-2023-08-08%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emissed%20debt%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20Evergrande%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-evergrande-property-developer-chapter-15-bankruptcy-protection-2023-8%5C%22%3Efiled%20for%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-recession-inflation-deflation-xi-jinping-stimulus-cpi-ppi-2023-8%5C%22%3EChina%20tipped%20into%20deflation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20observers%20have%20turned%20increasingly%20bearish%20on%20the%20country's%20growth%20outlook.%20But%20the%20government%20is%20extremely%20involved%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20Beijing%20consistently%20prioritizes%20stability%2C%20which%20suggests%20a%20cascading%2C%20Lehman-esque%20fallout%20would%20be%20limited%20in%20scope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrying%20to%20compare%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20China%20now%20to%20the%20US%20in%202008%20is%20like%20comparing%20apples%20and%20oranges%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicholas%20Spiro%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20macroeconomic%20consultancy%20Lauressa%20Advisory%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20unhelpful%20but%20it's%20made%20its%20way%20into%20the%20narrative%2C%20which%20is%20worrying.%20It's%20not%20a%20Lehman%20moment.%20You're%20not%20going%20to%20have%20a%20comparable%20banking%20crisis%20because%20of%20the%20simple%20reason%20you%20have%20a%20state-owned%20financial%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Spiro%20said%20it's%20unlikely%20China%20can%20return%20to%20the%20boom-times%20of%20decades%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20isn't%20going%20to%20be%20a%20sudden%20sharp%20shock%20or%20dramatic%20loss%20of%20confidence%20or%20financial%20stability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BRather%2C%20it'll%20be%20a%20slow-moving%2C%20structural%20economic%20crisis%20that%20could%20last%20for%20years.%20We%20are%20seeing%20a%20deep-seated%2C%20economic%20malaise%20which%20will%20be%20very%20prolonged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-beijing-lehman-moment-policy-deflation-economy-markets-property-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693052102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e78bc852bc2d0019916bd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-beijing-lehman-moment-policy-deflation-economy-markets-property-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Beijing%20is%20dealing%20with%20ballooning%20asset%20bubbles%20and%20a%20shaky%20housing%20sector%2C%20but%20economists%20say%20the%20comparison%20to%202008%20is%20overblown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22prosen%40insider.com%20(Phil%20Rosen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-beijing-lehman-moment-policy-deflation-economy-markets-property-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20Has%20Failed%20in%20Manipur%3A%20World%20Meitei%20Council%20Chair%20Heigrujam%20Nabashyam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26174330%2FKT-26-August.00_49_23_19.Still003.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20strong%20criticism%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%20and%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20effective%20response%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20World%20Meitei%20Council%2C%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20says%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20prime%20minister%20has%20failed%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%20Heigrujam%20Nabashyam%20says%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20if%20he%20wants%2C%20can%20restore%20order%20and%20peace%20in%2024%20hours%20but%20has%20failed%20to%20do%20so.%20Nabashyam%20called%20this%20%E2%80%9Cirresponsible%E2%80%9D%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20is%20often%20argumentative%20and%20quarrelsome%2C%20Nabashyam%20began%20by%20saying%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20could%20have%20nipped%20the%20problem%20in%20the%20bud%20in%20the%20first%2024%20hours%20but%20failed%20to%20act.%20He%20said%20during%20the%20critical%20first%20dew%20days%20in%20May%20the%20state%20government%20was%20not%20just%20ineffective%20but%20non-existent.%20However%2C%20Nabashyam%20said%20he%20cannot%20say%20why%20Biren%20Singh%20failed%20to%20act%20and%2C%20despite%20repeated%20questioning%2C%20refused%20to%20accept%20this%20failure%20to%20act%20is%20incompetence.%20He%20also%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20chief%20minister%20should%20be%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thrust%20of%20Nabashyam%E2%80%99s%20argument%20was%20not%20to%20blame%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20who%20he%20considers%20%E2%80%9Ca%20proxy%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20both%20the%20home%20minister%20and%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%20Nabashyam%20did%20not%20accept%20criticisms%20of%20the%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20speech%20made%20by%20several%20Kuki%20organisations%20as%20well%20as%20seven%20BJP%20Kuki%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhilst%20Nabashyam%20sympathised%20with%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20Meitei%20Pangal%20community%2C%20who%20feel%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20shattered%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20insecure%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20did%20not%20accept%20that%20recent%20statements%20by%20the%20United%20Naga%20Council%2C%20which%20appear%20to%20tilt%20towards%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20make%20the%20situation%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FxheFhV5OB_Y%3Fsi%3DOgoT9sSAxLCVZTje%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693052082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26174330%2FKT-26-August.00_49_23_19.Still003.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fprime-minister-modi-has-failed-in-manipur-world-meitei-council-chair-heigrujam-nabashyam%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heigrujam%20Nabashyam%20says%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20if%20he%20wants%2C%20can%20restore%20order%20and%20peace