22%3Ethe%20day%20the%20crypto%20exchange%20FTX%20crashed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20was%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20days%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20really%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20do%20afterwards%2C%20until%20I%20discovered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20making%20six-figures%20teaching%20people%20how%20to%20use%20the%20AI%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20crypto%20trader%20and%20investor%20for%20over%20six%20years.%20I%20used%20FTX%20for%20most%20of%20my%20trading%2C%20and%20I%20put%20more%20funds%20into%20my%20account%20right%20around%20the%20time%20the%20platform%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20lost%20all%20my%20money%2C%20I%20thought%20%26quot%3BScrew%20this%20whole%20crypto%20thing.%26quot%3B%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20with%20content%2C%20but%20it%20was%20tough%20to%20stay%20motivated.%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20rebuild.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20after%20the%20crash%2C%20OpenAI%20launched%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20it%20really%20caught%20my%20interest.%20Like%20with%20crypto%2C%20I've%20fallen%20down%20rabbit%20holes%20where%20I%20would%20completely%20immerse%20myself%20all%20day%20into%20one%20activity%2C%20and%20as%20a%20trader%2C%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20spot%20trends%20and%20new%20developments%20early%20on.%20AI%20just%20happened%20to%20be%20the%20next%20big%20thing%2C%20so%20I%20thought%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20could%20do%20that%20all%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20in%20January%2C%20I%20was%20playing%20around%20with%20ChatGPT%20all%20the%20time.%20That%20month%20was%20also%20around%20the%20time%20I%20started%20to%20experiment%20with%20posting%20content%20about%20AI%20on%20my%20personal%20Twitter%20to%20see%20what%20landed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonths%20later%2C%20I%20got%20much%20better%20at%20using%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20in%20April%2C%20I%20created%20a%20new%20Twitter%20page%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faisolopreneur%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20Solopreneur%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20offers%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20increase%20productivity.%20I%20specifically%20tailored%20my%20content%20to%20solopreneurs%20%E2%80%94%20entrepreneurs%20who%20run%20a%20business%20without%20any%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20since%20everybody%20was%20doing%20AI%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20help%20from%20ChatGPT%2C%20I%20wrote%20multiple%20Twitter%20threads%20a%20day%20on%20AI-related%20topics%20like%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faisolopreneur%2Fstatus%2F1645763930424221701%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20ChatGPT%20prompts%20that%20could%20increase%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faisolopreneur%2Fstatus%2F1646488709632598018%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI-tools%20that%20could%20save%20hours%20of%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20which%20racked%20up%20millions%20of%20views.%20Sixty-five%20days%20later%2C%20I%20got%20to%20100%2C000%20followers%2C%20and%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faisolopreneur.beehiiv.com%2Fsubscribe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20separate%20AI%20Solopreneurship%20newsletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20go%20along%20with%20the%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20following%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20some%20of%20my%20followers%20wanted%20to%20know%20what%20AI%20and%20prompts%20I%20use%20to%20help%20improve%20my%20content%20and%20drive%20traffic%20to%20my%20page%2C%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20going%20to%20launch%20a%20course%20on%20this%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20exactly%20what%20I%20did.%20Starting%20in%20June%2C%20I%20worked%20on%20the%20course%20for%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20every%20single%20day%2C%20which%20was%20stressful.%20Two%20months%20later%2C%20in%20early%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faisolopreneur.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20Audience%20Accelerator%20course%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20teaches%20solopreneurs%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20create%20content%20that%20could%20help%20market%20their%20businesses%2C%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20fears%20that%20the%20course%20wouldn't%20take%20off.%20A%20similar%20course%20that%20launched%20before%20mine%20didn't%20do%20well%2C%20and%20there%20are%20so%20many%20free%20AI%20courses%20online.%20I%20wondered%20if%20people%20would%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20mine%2C%20which%20starts%20at%20%24179.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20surprise%2C%20the%20launch%20went%20really%20well.%20In%20less%20than%20a%20month%2C%20I%20got%201%2C078%20orders%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20solopreneurs%2C%20content%20creators%2C%20and%20crypto%20people%20in%20their%20early%2020s%20to%20mid%2030s%20based%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20%E2%80%94%20and%20made%20%24176%2C885%20in%20gross%20revenue.%20This%20all%20happened%20crazy%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20course%20resonated%20with%20people%20because%20they%20want%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20save%20time%20on%20certain%20tasks%20so%20they%20can%20focus%20on%20running%20their%20business.%20Everyone%20says%20you%20have%20to%20create%20content%20to%20get%20customers%2C%20but%20most%20people%20don't%20have%20the%20time%20or%20frameworks%20for%20how%20to%20do%20that.%20AI%20is%20really%20a%20good%20way%20to%20solve%20these%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20call%20myself%20an%20AI%20expert.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20hate%20that%20word.%20I%20simply%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20create%20my%20content%2C%20and%20continued%20to%20teach%20myself%20how%20to%20most%20effectively%20use%20the%20chatbot%20for%20that%20purpose%20as%20I%20crafted%20the%20course.%20Ultimately%2C%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20share%20my%20learnings%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%205%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20use%20generative%20AI%20to%20grow%20your%20social%20media%20presence%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Focus%20on%20learning%20no%20more%20than%20two%20AI%20tools%20at%20once%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I've%20seen%20people%20try%20out%2010%20tools%20at%20a%20time%20and%20end%20up%20using%20none%20of%20them.%20I%20choose%20to%20focus%20on%20ChatGPT%20and%20Anthropic's%20chatbot%20called%20Claude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Be%20specific%20about%20what%20you%20want%20and%20don't%20want%20in%20your%20content%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20crafting%20your%20prompt%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20include%20specifics%20like%20the%20format%2C%20context%2C%20target%20audience%2C%20tone%20of%20voice%20you%20want%20to%20see%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20constraints%20on%20what%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20%E2%80%94in%20your%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Train%20ChatGPT%20on%20past%20content%20that%20performed%20well%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Feed%20the%20chatbot%20a%20piece%20of%20content%2C%20like%20an%20X%20thread%2C%20then%20ask%20it%20to%20learn%20from%20that%20example%20and%20to%20restructure%20the%20idea%20you're%20giving%20it%20based%20on%20the%20example's%20format%20and%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Talk%20to%20ChatGPT%20as%20if%20they%20were%20your%20employee%20or%20intern%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20writing%20your%20prompt%2C%20ask%20yourself%20%26quot%3BHow%20would%20I%20explain%20what%20I%20need%20to%20my%20content%20writers%26quot%3B%20and%20talk%20to%20ChatGPT%20in%20that%20same%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5)%20Create%20with%20AI%2C%20but%20edit%20manually%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEven%20though%20I've%20used%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20optimize%20my%20content%2C%20the%20magic%20comes%20when%20you%20flex%20your%20writing%20skills%20and%20tweak%20the%20generated%20response%20to%20give%20it%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-former-crypto-trader-made