eggs%20on%20other%20students%20to%20slap%20him%20for%20not%20doing%20his%20homework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20declared%20it%20-%20all%20Muslim%20children%20should%20be%20beaten%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20the%20principal%20of%20Neha%20Public%20School%20to%20someone%20not%20on%20camera.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoud%20slaps%20are%20heard%20as%20the%20students%20follow%20their%20teacher's%20instruction.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20you%20hit%20harder%3F%20Whose%20turn%20is%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20says%20in%20the%20wrenching%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20was%20forced%20to%20stand%20for%20hours%2C%20humiliated%20and%20beaten%2C%20his%20father%20told%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20son%20is%20seven.%20The%20teacher%20had%20my%20child%20beaten%20up%20repeatedly%20by%20students.%20My%20nephew%20made%20the%20video%2C%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20school%20for%20some%20work...%20My%20seven-year-old%20was%20tortured%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20two.%20He%20is%20scared.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20Hindu-Muslim%20issue.%20We%20want%20the%20law%20to%20take%20its%20own%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20boy's%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20is%20in%20shock%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20didn't%20report%20the%20crime%20earlier.%20When%20the%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20police%20registered%20a%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20done%20a%20full%20investigation.%20On%20the%20complaint%20of%20the%20child's%20father%2C%20we%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20accused%20teacher%2C%20departmental%20action%20is%20also%20being%20taken%20against%20the%20teacher.%20Counselling%20of%20the%20child%20and%20his%20family%20is%20also%20being%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Arvind%20Mallappa%2C%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20Muzaffarnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20police%20officer%20claimed%20after%20a%20probe%2C%20they%20had%20established%20that%20the%20teacher%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mothers%20of%20those%20Muslim%20children%20who%20do%20not%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20studies%20of%20their%20wards%2C%20their%20academics%20get%20totally%20destroyed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20principal%20sought%20to%20defend%20her%20egregious%20act%20and%20also%20claimed%20the%20video%20was%20edited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20live%20in%20Hindu-Muslim%20harmony.%20Many%20students%20in%20our%20school%20are%20Muslims.%20That%20child%20did%20not%20bring%20his%20homework%20that%20day%2C%20I%20said%20in%20the%20video%20that%20Muhammedan%20mothers%20should%20not%20take%20their%20children%20to%20their%20maternal%20uncle's%20house%20as%20exams%20are%20approaching.%20But%20they%20made%20this%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20pressure%20from%20the%20child's%20parents%20to%20be%20strict%20with%20him.%20I%20am%20handicapped%2C%20so%20I%20made%20some%20students%20slap%20him%20up%20so%20that%20he%20would%20start%20doing%20his%20homework%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bminor%20issue%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThis%20wasn't%20my%20intention.%20They%20all%20are%20like%20my%20kids%20and%20I%20am%20accepting%20my%20mistake%2C%20but%20this%20was%20unnecessarily%20turned%20into%20a%20big%20issue.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20politicians%20that%20this%20was%20a%20small%20matter.%20Leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20have%20tweeted%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20such%20a%20big%20thing%20to%20tweet%20about.%20How%20will%20teachers%20teach%20if%20daily%20issues%20like%20these%20are%20made%20viral%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20provoked%20a%20political%20furore%20with%20the%20Congress%20targeting%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20ruling%20BJP.%20UP's%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Brijesh%20Pathak%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20cognizance%20and%20full%20action%20will%20be%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20development%20on%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Naresh%20Tikait%20claimed%20he%20had%20brokered%20a%20compromise%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20communal%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693048680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fk4qv3fhg_up-student_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmuzaffarnagar-news%2Fschoolboy-beaten-for-an-hour-up-schools-slap-muslim-classmate-horror-4331773%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20schoolteacher%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20faces%20tough%20charges%20after%20she%20was%20seen%20ordering%20her%20students%20to%20slap%20their%20Muslim%20classmate%20in%20a%20viral%20video%20that%20has%20triggered%20widespread%20outrage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmuzaffarnagar-news%2Fschoolboy-beaten-for-an-hour-up-schools-slap-muslim-classmate-horror-4331773%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmuzaffarnagar-news%2Fschoolboy-beaten-for-an-hour-up-schools-slap-muslim-classmate-horror-4331773%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmuzaffarnagar-news%2Fschoolboy-beaten-for-an-hour-up-schools-slap-muslim-classmate-horror-4331773%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22High-income%20Americans%20rarely%20mix%20with%20poorer%20people.%20Restaurants%20like%20Applebee's%20and%20Olive%20Garden%20are%20the%20exception.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224444%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sign%20outside%20an%20Olive%20Garden%20restaurant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6390824cad2cb500189ee3b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20manager%20of%20an%20Olive%20Garden%20in%20Kansas%20gave%20staff%20a%20blunt%20ultimatum.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmericans%20are%20even%20less%20likely%20to%20mix%20with%20people%20from%20different%20socio-economic%20classes%20than%20pre-pandemic.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe're%20working%20remotely%20and%20shopping%20online%20more%2C%20and%20venturing%20outside%20of%20our%20own%20neighborhoods%20less.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENew%20research%20shows%20that%20affordable%2C%20chain%20restaurants%20are%20the%20exception.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20meet%20someone%20making%20a%20lot%20more%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20lot%20less%20%E2%80%94%20money%20than%20you%2C%20try%20your%20local%20full-service%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20really%3A%20Restaurant%20chains%20like%20Olive%20Garden%20and%20Applebee's%20are%20America's%20socioeconomic%20melting%20pot%2C%20according%20to%20new%20research.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4516850%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Maxim%20Massenhoff%20and%20Nathan%20Wilmers%2C%20of%20the%20Naval%20Postgraduate%20School%20and%20Harvard%20University%2C%20respectively%2C%20looks%20at%20where%20Americans%20of%20different%20classes%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20rub%20shoulders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20socio-economically%20diverse%20places%20in%20America%20are%20not%20public%20institutions%2C%20like%20schools%20and%20parks%2C%20but%20affordable%2C%20chain%20restaurants%2C%26quot%3B%20Massenhoff%20and%20Wilmers%20write.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20used%20SafeGraph%20mobile%20location%20data%20that%20tracks%20how%20many%20people%20are%20at%20certain%20places%20and%20where%20those%20people%20live%2C%20which%20can%20be%20indicative%20of%20income.%20Using%20that%20data%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20see%20how%20many%20visitors%20from%20varying%20income%20brackets%20frequent%20different%20establishments%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20isolated%20Americans%20of%20different%20classes%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBroadly%2C%20Americans%20are%20pretty%20isolated%20by%20class.%20The%20researchers%20find%20that%20the%20wealthiest%20Americans%20are%20far%20and%20away%20more%20likely%20to%20encounter%20just%20similarly%20high-earning%20peers%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20rich%20hang%20out%20with%20the%20rich.%20And%20isolation%20across%20class%20is%20more%20pronounced%20in%20urban%20and%20suburban%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20socio-economic%20isolation%20has%20grown%20even%20more%20stark%20since%20the%20pandemic.%20Researchers%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-mix-less-with-people-in-different-incomes-since-pandemic-2023-5%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20far%20fewer%20people%20visited%20neighborhoods%20where%20residents%20made%20significantly%20more%20or%20less%20money%20than%20they%20did%20in%20December%202021%20than%20in%20January%202019.%20Interactions%20between%20people%20of%20different%20socioeconomic%20backgrounds%20dropped%20by%20up%20to%2030%25%20during%20that%20time%20period%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0long%20after%20COVID%20lockdowns%20were%20lifted%2C%20according%20to%20tracked%20cellphone%20data%20of%20more%20than%20a%20million%20people%20in%20Boston%2C%20Dallas%2C%20Seattle%2C%20and%20Los%20Angeles.%20The%20researchers%20laid%20the%20blame%20in%20part%20on%20the%20rise%20of%20remote%20work%20and%20online%20shopping%20in%20helping%20keep%20Americans%20in%20their%20own%20neighborhoods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20some%20places%20where%20Americans%20of%20different%20incomes%20congregate%3A%20The%20aforementioned%20chain%20restaurants.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20sweet%20spot%20for%20cross-class%20mixing%20is%20what%20the%20researchers%20call%20%26quot%3Bfull-service%2C%20low-price%20restaurants.%26quot%3B%20That%20includes%20places%20like%20IHOP%2C%20Applebee's%2C%20Chili's%2C%20and%2C%20yes%2C%20Olive%20Garden.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20businesses%2C%20like%20pharmacies%2C%20grocery%20stores%2C%20and%20gyms%2C%20or%20public%20institutions%2C%20like%20parks%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20libraries%2C%20are%20not%20as%20diverse%2C%20as%20they%20tend%20to%20serve%20the%20people%20in%20their%20immediate%20vicinity%2C%20the%20researchers%20found.%20A%20higher-income%20person%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20meet%20a%20lower-income%20person%20at%20a%20fast%20food%20restaurant%20like%20McDonald's%20or%20Wendy's.%20However%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20reciprocal%20effect%20since%20those%20restaurants%20tend%20to%20see%20much%20more%20of%20the%20latter.%20At%20somewhere%20like%20Panera%2C%20poorer%20Americans%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20meet%20non-poor%20Americans%2C%20but%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20researchers%20note%2C%20all%20of%20that%20could%20mean%20rethinking%20policy%20situations%20for%20getting%20Americans%20from%20different%20income%20brackets%20to%20socialize%2C%20especially%20as%20some%20areas%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eater.com%2F2013%2F4%2F2%2F6457573%2Fnew-york-town-bans-fast-casual-restaurants%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprioritized%20cutting%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsfplanning.org%2Fproject%2Fpolicy-basis-formula-retail-chain-stores%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFormula%2520retail%2520uses%2520are%2520commonly%2Ctwo%2520or%2520more%2520of%2520the%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enumber%20of%20chain%20restaurants%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20allow.%20After%20all%2C%20research%20from%20Harvard%20economist%20Raj%20Chetty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwant-to-get-rich-make-rich-friends-harvard-reserach-study-2022-8%5C%22%3Ehas%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20being%20friends%20with%20higher-earners%20is%20key%20to%20your%20economic%20mobility%20%E2%80%94%20but%20many%20lower-earning%20Americans%20make%20friends%20based%20on%20proximity.%20That's%20why%20cross-income%20areas%20for%20socializing%20are%20important.%20You%20might%20just%20meet%20that%20rich%20new%20friend%20at%20Chili's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-poor-americans-mix-most-chains-applebees-olive-garden-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693048501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e8caf1a7adf7001908035d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-poor-americans-mix-most-chains-applebees-olive-garden-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20friends%20who%20make%20more%20than%20you%20is%20an%20important%20boost%20for%20economic%20mobility.%20You%20might%20find%20them%20at%20Chili's%20or%20IHOP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan%2CEliza%20Relman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-poor-americans-mix-most-chains-applebees-olive-garden-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22200%20monster%20hunters%20armed%20with%20drones%20join%20the%20biggest%20search%20in%2050%20years%20for%20Scotland's%20fabled%20Loch%20Ness%20creature%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20and%20white%20image%20showing%20what%20looks%20like%20a%20creature's%20head%20and%20neck%20in%20the%20Loch%20Ness.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e9b484b413420019a3ee6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221650%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%201934%20%26quot%3Bsurgeon's%20photo%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20monster%2C%20now%20deemed%20a%20hoax%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E200%20volunteers%20are%20searching%20for%20the%20Loch%20Ness%20monster%20this%20weekend.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20operation%20in%20the%20Scottish%20Highlands%20is%20the%2