cial%20confirmed%20that%20industrialist%20and%20Kuber%20Group%20director%20Vikas%20Malu%20was%20among%20the%20three%20occupants%20of%20the%20Rolls-Royce%20that%20smashed%20into%20a%20petrol%20tanker%20at%20an%20extremely%20high%20speed.%20Mr%20Malu%20is%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Gurugram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20three%20people%20in%20the%20tanker%20-%20the%20driver%20and%20his%20assistant%20-%20were%20killed%20when%20the%20Rolls-Royce%20Phantom%20rammed%20it%20on%20the%20New%20Delhi-Mumbai%20expressway%20in%20Nuh.%20Barring%20the%20driver%2C%20all%20of%20the%20car's%20occupants%20have%20been%20hospitalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Nuh%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Narendra%20Bijaraniya%20said%20that%20the%20entire%20stretch%20of%20the%20expressway%20is%20lined%20with%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20that%20the%20police%20are%20scanning%20the%20footage.%20The%20truck%2C%20he%20said%2C%20took%20a%20U-turn%20on%20the%20highway%20and%20the%20Phantom%20was%20travelling%20at%20a%20very%20high%20speed%20when%20the%20two%20collided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20tracked%20down%20the%20third%20occupant%20of%20the%20tanker%2C%20Gautam%2C%20who%20is%20recovering%20from%20his%20injuries%20at%20his%20house%20in%20Haryana's%20Ujina.%20Gautam%2C%20who%20was%20sitting%20next%20to%20the%20driver%20and%20the%20assistant%2C%20said%20the%20truck%20was%20taking%20a%20U-turn%20when%20it%20was%20rammed%20by%20the%20Rolls-Royce.%20Struggling%20to%20speak%20because%20of%20his%20injuries%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Phantom's%20speed%20was%20at%20least%20190%20km%2Fhr%20and%20the%20truck%20overturned%20after%20being%20hit%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20car%20was%20at%20fault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20from%20the%20crash%20site%20showed%20little%20left%20of%20the%20Phantom%20priced%20at%20over%20Rs%2010%20crore.%20The%20front%20of%20the%20car%20was%20completely%20mangled%2C%20the%20engine%20was%20abla