c%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F02142235%2FIMG_0750-e1643792690720.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20scrolled%20through%20my%20social%20media%20feed%2C%20I%20watched%20an%20endearing%20video%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20listening%20intently%20while%20a%20Greek%20child%20sang%20in%20Hindi.%20His%20face%20beamed%20with%20joy%20and%20pride%20as%20he%20interacted%20with%20the%20little%20girl.%20Little%20did%20she%20know%20that%20thousands%20of%20miles%20away%2C%20in%20a%20remote%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20schoolboy%20trembled%20as%20his%20teacher%20egged%20his%20classmates%20to%20slap%20him.%20Though%20his%20face%20was%20streaked%20with%20tears%2C%20the%20teacher%20taunted%20a%20classmate%20for%20not%20raining%20blows%20hard%20enough%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20boy%20being%20slapped%20was%20Muslim%20and%20that%20the%20teacher%20made%20a%20sweeping%2C%20derogatory%20reference%20to%20Muslims%2C%20only%20added%20to%20the%20horrendous%20nature%20of%C2%A0%20the%20video%20seen%20on%20social%20media%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20public%20outrage%2C%20the%20police%20visited%20the%20school%20in%20Muzzafarnagar%20district%20and%20said%20it%20would%20take%20appropriate%20action.%20Of%20course%2C%20had%20the%20victim%20been%20a%20Hindu%20and%20the%20perpetrator%20a%20Muslim%2C%20the%20teacher%20would%20have%20been%20promptly%20arrested%20and%20their%20home%20bulldozed%20by%20an%20eager%20state%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20too%20scared%20or%20weary%20to%20initiate%20action%20is%20emblematic%20of%20the%20eroding%20trust%20between%20minorities%20and%20the%20legal%20institutions%20responsible%20for%20protecting%20them.%20He%20took%20the%20only%20recourse%20available%20by%20forbidding%20his%20son%20to%20attend%20school.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20the%20result%20that%20those%20consumed%20with%20the%20bigotry%20of%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20hoped%20for.%20This%20is%20precisely%20what%20happened%20after%20the%20%E2%80%98hijab%20controversy%E2%80%99%20in%20Karnataka%20that%20led%20to%20many%20Muslim%20families%20discontinuing%20their%20daughters%E2%80%99%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20has%20already%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onmanorama.com%2Fcareer-and-campus%2Ftop-news%2F2023%2F02%2F15%2Fdrastic-cut-in-central-scholarship-fellowship-funds.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecancelled%20many%20of%20the%20scholarships%20earmarked%20for%20minorities%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20crucial%20step%20in%20the%20path%20to%20their%20empowerment%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20flames%20of%20hatred%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20actively%20fanned%20since%202014%20are%20now%20threatening%20to%20singe%20the%20safe%20sanctuary%20of%20our%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20the%20so-called%20mother%20of%20democracy%20get%20to%20this%20abhorrent%20point%3F%20As%20if%20engineered%20riots%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20modus%20operandi%20to%20sow%20division%20now%20includes%20propaganda%20through%20movies%20steeped%20in%20disinformation%20and%20demonisation%20of%20Muslims.%20Otherwise%20what%20explains%20a%20slew%20of%20anti-Muslim%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20files%2C%2072%20Hoorain%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EKerala%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20promoted%20by%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%3F%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Files%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20vilified%20all%20Kashmiri%20Muslims%2C%20was%20recently%20awarded%20a%20prestigious%20official%20prize%20for%20%E2%80%98national%20integration%E2%80%99!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20country%20we%20have%20become%2C%20shocking%20incidents%20against%20minorities%20which%20should%20have%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20shame%20for%20everyone%20are%20instead%20being%20glorified%20and%20turned%20into%2