20parents%20did%20not%20want%20to%20complain%20then.%20But%20on%20Saturday%20morning%20they%20came%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20made%20a%20complaint%2C%20and%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBenarasiyaa%2Fstatus%2F1695329012854489349%5C%22%3EBangari%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-teacher-forces-fellow-students-to-slap-muslim-child-ncpcr-orders-not-to-circulate-video%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20earlier%20hesitant%20to%20approach%20the%20police%20because%20he%20did%20not%20think%20he%20would%20be%20properly%20heard.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20outrage%20on%20social%20media%20grew%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20take%20action%20as%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20happening%20to%20other%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20around%209%20am%20on%20August%2024%2C%20the%20child%20was%20reportedly%20subjected%20to%20assault%20by%20other%20students%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20teacher.%20Sources%20close%20to%20the%20child%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ci%3EWire%3C%2Fi%3E%20that%20he%20was%20assaulted%20while%20the%20teacher%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CMohammedans%20should%20be%20beaten%20up%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20video%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20several%20children%20can%20be%20seen%20slapping%20the%20crying%20child%2C%20with%20Tyagi%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20declared%20that%20all%20those%20Mohammadan%20%5Bi.e.%20Muslim%5D%20children%20should%20be%E2%80%A6(inaudible).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20opposition%20leaders%20have%20expressed%20outrage%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20also%20blamed%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20was%20creating%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20hate%20and%20communal%20violence%20that%20is%20leading%20to%20such%20incidents.%20%E2%80%9CSowing%20the%20poison%20of%20discrimination%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20innocent%20children%2C%20turning%20a%20holy%20place%20like%20school%20into%20a%20marketplace%20of%20hatred%20%E2%80%93%20nothing%20worse%20a%20teacher%20can%20do%20for%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20the%20same%20kerosene%20spread%20by%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20set%20every%20corner%20of%20India%20on%20fire.%20Children%20are%20the%20future%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20do%20not%20hate%20them%2C%20we%20all%20have%20to%20teach%20love%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20poison%20of%20the%20divisive%20thinking%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20spread%20so%20much%20in%20the%20society%20that%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20an%20education%20teacher%2C%20Tripta%20Tyagi%2C%20is%20teaching%20the%20lesson%20of%20religious%20hatred%20since%20childhood%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20security%20personnel%20RPF%20jawan%2C%20Chetan%20Kumar%2C%20is%20killing%20innocent%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20leader%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20also%20questioned%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20and%20its%20chief%20Priyank%20Kangoo.%20As%20a%20first%20response%2C%20Kangoo%20had%20insisted%20that%20videos%20of%20the%20incident%20be%20removed%20from%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20video%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%20where%20a%20teacher%20is%20asking%20her%20students%20to%20slap%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20is%20a%20product%20of%20the%20last%209%20years.%20The%20message%20being%20drilled%20into%20the%20minds%20of%20little%20children%20is%20that%20one%20can%20beat%20up%20%26amp%3B%20humiliate%20a%20Muslim%20without%20any%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20(%40asadow