%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F02191508%2FParchment-bg.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Though%20the%20Union%20government%C2%A0received%20256%20applications%20for%20the%20posts%20of%20information%20commissioners%20in%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20(CIC)%2C%20no%20appointments%20have%20been%20made%20in%20eight%20months%20to%20fill%20up%20vacancies%20in%20the%20statutory%20body%20which%20is%20already%20working%20below%20half%20its%20capacity.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20all%20the%20incumbent%20commissioners%20are%20set%20to%20demit%20office%20by%20the%20end%20of%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20information%20was%20revealed%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%2024%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20query%20filed%20by%20Commodore%20(Retired)%20Lokesh%20Batra.%20In%20December%202022%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fgovt-invites-applications-for-information-commissioners-in-cic-news-246971%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20eligible%20applicants%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20posts%20of%20information%20commissioners%20(not%20exceeding%20six).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadline%20for%20application%20was%20January%2012%2C%202023%2C%20by%20which%20time%20the%20DoPT%20received%20256%20applications.%20In%20addition%2C%2012%20persons%20sent%20their%20applications%20after%20the%20deadline%20had%20passed.%20Though%20eight%20months%20have%20passed%20since%20the%20deadline%2C%20no%20appointments%20have%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Commodore%20Batra%E2%80%99s%20RTI%20query%2C%20the%20DoPT%20gave%20details%20of%20the%20search%20and%20selection%20process%20and%20that%20the%20particulars%20of%20applicants%20were%20tabulated%20by%20it%20and%20sent%20to%20a%20search%20committee%20constituted%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20headed%20by%20the%20cabinet%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGovt%20got%20256%20applications%20for%20posts%20of%20information%20commissioners%20at%20CIC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENames%20of%20256%20Applicants%20for%20ICs%20-Advt%20dt%2020.12.2022%20%2B%3Cbr%3E%5Cnnames%20of%2012%20late%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20we%20know%20any%20one%20of%20the%20name%20in%20the%20list%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%20RTI%20Response.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSRleYUCDc0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSRleYUCDc0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20CommodoreLokeshBatra%20(%40CommodoreBatra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCommodoreBatra%2Fstatus%2F1695328014610190506%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppointments%20are%20finalised%20by%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20comprising%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20a%20Union%20cabinet%20minister.%20The%20persons%20who%20are%20recommended%20by%20the%20committee%20are%20appointed%20to%20the%20CIC%20by%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CIC%20is%20the%20highest%20appellate%20authority%20in%20RTI%20matters%20concerning%20the%20Union%20government.%20As%20against%20the%20total%20strength%20of%20one%20chief%20information%20commissioner%20and%20ten%20information%20commissioners%2C%20it%20is%20functioning%20with%20one%20chief%20information%20commissioner%20and%20four%20information%20commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tenure%20of%20chief%20information%20commissioner%20Y.K.%20Sinha%20will%20end%20on%20October%203.%20The%20remaining%20information%20commissioners%20%E2%80%94%20Suresh%20Chandra%2C%20Uday%20Mahurkar%2C%20Heeralal%20Samariya%20and%20Saroj%20Punhani%20%E2%80%94%20will%20leave%20office%20in%20November%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovt-got-256-applications-for-posts-of-information-commissioners-at-cic-reveals-rti-reply%2F1729320%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520its%2520response%2520to%2520an%2Ccommissioners%2520(not%2520exceeding%2520six).%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERTI%20activists%20have%20long%20protested%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20attempts%20to%20dilute%20the%20landmark%20transparency%20law.%20The%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%20passed%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20will%20further%20reduce%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%2C%20activists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fregressive-amendments-to-rti-act-ncpri-flags-concerns-over-digital-personal-data-protection-bill%5C%22%3Ehave%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Recently%2C%20years%20of%20information%20stored%20on%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20portal%20for%20RTI%20applications%20%E2%80%9Cdisappeared%E2%80%9D%20suddenly.%20After%20activists%20raised%20an%20alarm%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frti-portal-rtionline-years-of-information-disappears%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20website%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20maintenance%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Carchival%20data%20will%20be%20available%20soon%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693038542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F02191508%2FParchment-bg.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcic-applications-no-new-appointments%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20advertisement%20was%20issued%20to%20fill%20up%20vacancies%20in%20the%20statutory%20body%20eight%20months%20ago.%20The%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20is%20already%20working%20below%20half%20its%20capacity%20and%20all%20the%20incumbent%20commissioners%20are%20set%20to%20demit%20office%20by%20the%20end%20of%20November.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcic-applications-no-new-appointments%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFemale%20Robot%20'Vyommitra'%20Will%20Go%20To%20Space%26quot%3B%3A%20Science%20Minister%20On%20Gaganyaan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20send%20a%20female%20robot%20%26quot%3BVyommitra%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20said%20at%20the%20NDTV%20G20%20Conclave%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20a%20trial%20spaceflight%20will%20be%20attempted%20in%20the%20first%20or%20second%20week%20of%20October.%20In%20the%20subsequent%20mission%2C%20the%20female%20robot%20%26quot%3BVyommitra%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20space%2C%20said%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Science%20and%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Gaganyaan%20project%20got%20delayed%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%20Now%20we%20are%20planning%20the%20first%20trial%20mission%20in%20October%20first%20or%20second%20week.%20Bringing%20back%20the%20astronauts%20is%20as%20important%20as%20sending%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20second%20mission%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20female%20robot%20and%20she%20will%20mimic%20all%20human%20activities.%20If%20everything%20goes%20perfect%2C%20then%20we%20can%20have%20a%20go-ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20narrated%20the%20relief%20they%20felt%20when%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20lander%20finally%20touched%20down%20near%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20have%20been%20very%20closely%20associated%20with%20the%20ISRO%20team%2C%20we%20nervous.%20My%20first%20nervous%20moment%20was%20when%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20craft%20left%20Earth's%20orbit%20for%20the%20Moon's%20orbit...%20The%20landing%20was%20so%20smooth%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Moon%20landing%20was%20a%20quantum%20jump%20in%20the%20journey%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20and%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20happened%20because%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20threw%20open%20the%20space%20sector.%20Till%20about%202019%2C%20the%20gates%20of%20Sriharikota%20were%20closed%2C%20but%20this%20time%20the%20media%20and%20schoolchildren%20were%20invited.%20It%20was%20owned%20by%20the%20people%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20funding%20for%20the%20space%20programme%20has%20been%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20first%20nation%20to%20land%20a%20spacecraft%20near%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole%2C%20and%20the%20fourth%20nation%20to%20send%20a%20lander%20to%20the%20Moon%20successfully%20after%20the%20erstwhile%20USSR%2C%20the%20US%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693038120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fs0r2m5h_jitendra-singh-650_650x400_26_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffemale-robot-vyommitra-will-go-to-space-science-minister-on-gaganyaan-4331391%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20send%20a%20female%20robot%20%26quot%3BVyommitra%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20said%20at%20the%20NDTV%20G20%20Conclave%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffemale-robot-vyommitra-will-go-to-space-science-minister-on-gaganyaan-4331391%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffemale-robot-vyommitra-will-go-to-space-science-minister-on-gaganyaan-4331391%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffemale-robot-vyommitra-will-go-to-spac