Cbr%3E%5CnAsked%20about%20mass%20acceptability%20of%20the%20fuel%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20how%20the%20country%20switched%20from%20wood%20and%20coal%20to%20LPG%20cylinders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20getting%20gas%20cylinders%20were%20difficult%20and%20women%20used%20coal%20to%20cook%20food%20and%20it%20was%20toxic.%20We%20moved%20from%20there.%20Ujjawala%20scheme%20gave%20nine%20crore%20gas%20cylinders.%20The%20person%20who%20is%20most%20vulnerable%20is%20of%20the%20highest%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20cars%2C%20while%20the%20number%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20is%20going%20up%2C%20blending%20petrol%20with%20biofuels%20will%20reduce%20the%20dependence%20on%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22NDTV%20G20%20Conclave%20-%20watch%20live%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fdecoding-g20-ndtv-conclave-121%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22g20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fdecoding20-1200x738.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnical%20studies%20have%20shown%20that%20if%20there's%2020%25%20blending%20then%20auto%20parts%20won't%20have%20corrosion%2C%20parts%20will%20be%20better%20performance.%20I%20was%20told%20that%20you%20can't%20blend%20more%20than%2020%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Puri%2C%20who%20handles%20the%20Petroleum%20and%20Natural%20Gas%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20experimented%20that%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20problem%20till%2020%20per%20cent.%20E20%20fuel%20is%20right%20and%202%2C000%20pumps%20are%20selling%20E20%20fuel.%20If%20we%20put%20a%20target%20of%20over%2020%25%2C%20do%20have%20the%20system%20for%20that.%20Today%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%2C%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20cars%20are%20coming%20with%20E85%C2%A0%20--%20that%20is%2C%2085%20per%20cent%20ethanol%20in%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe