%20for%20observations%20of%20the%20Sun%20to%20be%20launched%20by%20the%20Bengaluru-headquartered%20space%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aditya-L1%20mission%2C%20aimed%20at%20studying%20the%20Sun%20from%20an%20orbit%20around%20the%20L1%2C%20would%20carry%20seven%20payloads%20to%20observe%20the%20photosphere%2C%20chromosphere%20and%20the%20outermost%20layers%20of%20the%20Sun%2C%20the%20corona%2C%20in%20different%20wavebands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20is%20a%20fully%20indigenous%20effort%20with%20the%20participation%20of%20national%20institutions%2C%20an%20ISRO%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengaluru-based%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIA)%20is%20the%20lead%20institute%20for%20the%20development%20of%20Visible%20Emission%20Line%20Coronagraph%20payload.%20While%20Inter-University%20Centre%20for%20Astronomy%20and%20Astrophysics%2C%20Pune%2C%20has%20developed%20the%20Solar%20Ultraviolet%20Imager%20payload%20for%20the%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20can%20provide%20observations%20on%20the%20corona%2C%20and%20on%20the%20solar%20Chromosphere%20using%20the%20UV%20payload%20and%20on%20the%20flares%20using%20the%20X-ray%20payloads.%20The%20particle%20detectors%20and%20the%20magnetometer%20payload%20can%20provide%20information%20on%20charged%20particles%20and%20the%20magnetic%20field%20reaching%20the%20halo%20orbit%20around%20L1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20satellite%2C%20realised%20at%20UR%20Rao%20Satellite%20Centre%20here%2C%20arrived%20at%20the%20ISRO's%20spaceport%20of%20Sriharikota%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20two%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20likely%20the%20launch%20will%20take%20place%20on%20September%202%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20ISRO%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spacecraft%20is%20planned%20to%20be%20placed%20in%20a%20halo%20orbit%20around%20the%20L1%20of%20the%20Sun-Earth%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20satellite%20placed%20in%20the%20halo%20orbit%20around%20the%20L1%20point%20has%20the%20major%20advantage%20of%20continuously%20viewing%20the%20Sun%20without%20any%20occultation%2Feclipses%2C%20ISRO%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20provide%20a%20greater%20advantage%20of%20observing%20the%20solar%20activities%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20space%20weather%20in%20real%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20special%20vantage%20point%20L1%2C%20four%20payloads%20directly%20view%20the%20Sun%20and%20the%20remaining%20three%20payloads%20carry%20out%20in-situ%20studies%20of%20particles%20and%20fields%20at%20the%20L1%2C%20thus%20providing%20important%20scientific%20studies%20of%20the%20propagatory%20effect%20of%20solar%20dynamics%20in%20the%20interplanetary%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20suits%20of%20Aditya%20L1%20payloads%20are%20expected%20to%20provide%20most%20crucial%20informations%20to%20understand%20the%20problem%20of%20coronal%20heating%2C%20coronal%20mass%20ejection%2C%20pre-flare%20and%20flare%20activities%20and%20their%20characteristics%2C%20dynamics%20of%20space%20weather%2C%20propagation%20of%20particle%20and%20fields%20etc%26quot%3B%2C%20ISRO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20science%20objectives%20of%20the%20Aditya-L1%20mission%20are%3A%20Study%20of%20Solar%20upper%20atmospheric%20(chromosphere%20and%20corona)%20dynamics%3B%20Study%20of%20chromospheric%20and%20coronal%20heating%2C%20physics%20of%20the%20partially%20ionised%20plasma%2C%20initiation%20of%20the%20coronal%20mass%20ejections%2C%20and%20flares%3B%20Observe%20the%20in-situ%20particle%20and%20plasma%20environment%20providing%20data%20for%20the%20study%20of%20particle%20dynamics%20from%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20include%20Physics%20of%20solar%20corona%20and%20its%20heating%20mechanism%3B%20Diagnostics%20of%20the%20coronal%20and%20coronal%20loops%20plasma%3A%20Temperature%2C%20velocity%20and%20density%3B%20Development%2C%20dynamics%20and%20origin%20of%20CMEs%3B%20Identify%20the%20sequence%20of%20processes%20that%20occur%20at%20multiple%20layers%20(chromosphere%2C%20base%20and%20extended%20corona)%20which%20eventually%20leads%20to%20solar%20eruptive%20events%3B%20Magnetic%20field%20topology%20and%20magnetic%20field%20measurements%20in%20the%20solar%20corona%3B%20Drivers%20for%20space%20weather%20(origin%2C%20composition%20and%20dynamics%20of%20solar%20wind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20instruments%20of%20Aditya-L1%20are%20tuned%20to%20observe%20the%20solar%20atmosphere%2C%20mainly%20the%20chromosphere%20and%20corona.%20In-situ%20instruments%20will%20observe%20the%20local%20environment%20at%20L1.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693035540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-02%2Fgq3kaabg_isro-launch-generic-pslv-launch-generic-ndtv-file-photo_625x300_05_February_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-aditya-l1-solar-mission-on-heels-of-chandrayaan-3-success-isro-eyes-september-2-for-mission-to-sun-4331337%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20successful%20moon%20lander%20venture%2C%20ISRO%20is%20now%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20solar%20mission%20in%20a%20week's%20time%2C%20likely%20on%20September%202%2C%20to%20study%20the%20Sun.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-aditya-l1-solar-mission-on-heels-of-chandrayaan-3-success-isro-eyes-september-2-for-mission-to-sun-4331337%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-aditya-l1-solar-mission-on-heels-of-chandrayaan-3-success-isro-eyes-september-2-for-mission-to-sun-4331337%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-aditya-l1-solar-mission-on-heels-of-chandrayaan-3-success-isro-eyes-september-2-for-mission-to-sun-4331337%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Veteran%20Bollywood%20Lyricist%20Dev%20Kohli%20Dies%20In%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVeteran%20Hindi%20film%20lyricist%20Dev%20Kohli%20died%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Saturday%2C%20He%20was%2080.%20Dev%20Kohli%20was%20famed%20for%20his%20songs%20in%20over%20100%20films%20including%20%3Ci%3EMaine%20Pyaar%20Kiya%2C%20Baazigar%2C%20Judwaa%202%2C%20Musafir%2C%20Shoot%20Out%20At%20Lokhandwala%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3ETaxi%20No.%209%202%2011%3C%2Fi%3E.%20He%20has%20collaborated%20with%20music%20directors%20like%20Anu%20Malik%2C%20Raam%20Laxman%2C%20Anand%20Raaj%20Anand%2C%20Anand%20Milind%20among%20others.%20Dev%20Kohli's%20spokesperson%20Pritam%20Sharma%20confirmed%20the%20lyricist%20died%20at%20his%20home%20early%20this%20morning.%20He%20had%20ailing%20for%20some%20months%20now%20and%20had%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20Kokilaben%20Hospital%20in%20Mumbai%20before%20being%20brought%20home%20around%2010%20days%20ago%2C%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDev%20Kohli's%20last%20rites%20will%20be%20conducted%20in%20Jogeshwari%20West%20around%206%20pm%20today.%20Close%20friends%20Anand%20Raaj%20Anand%2C%20Anu%20Malik%2C%20Uttam%20Singh%20along%20with%20stars%20from%20Bollywood%20will%20attend%20his%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Rawalpindi%2C%20Pakistan%20into%20a%20Sikh%20family%2C%20Kohli%20relocated%20to%20Dehradun%20following%20Partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDev%20Kohli's%20close%20friend%20composer%2C%20lyricist%20and%20playback%20singer%20Anand%20Raaj%20Anand%20told%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%201995%2C%20when%20I%20first%20arrived%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20got%20my%20first%20project%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20open%20a%20bank%20account%20but%20bank%20personnel%20said%20they%20could%20not%20do%20so%20unless%20i%20produced%20somebody%20who%20would%20vouch%20for%20me.%20At%20that%20moment%2C%20a%20sardar%20ji%20intervened%20and%20helped%20me.%20It%20was%20Dev%20Kohli%20ji.%20He%20told%20me%20You're%20into%20music%2C%20and%20I%20write%20music.%20Therefore%2C%20don't%20worry%20and%20he%20signed%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20two%20days%20I%20called%20him%20on%20his%20landline%20as%20I%20was%20excited%20and%20things%20were%20proceeding%20in%20a%20in%20a%20laid-back%20manner.%20Kohli%20ji%20invited%20me%20to%20sing%20as%20we%20got%20started%20playing.%20I%20informed%20him%20that%20I%20had%20also%20composed%20songs%20and%20he%20told%20me%20that%20he%20would%20write%20for%20me%20when%20I%20made%20it%20big.%20A%20few%20years%20later%2C%20his%20predictions%20came%20true%20and%20we%20ended%20up%20performing%20numerous%20tunes%20together.%20I%20only%20ever%20collaborated%20with%20one%20or%20two%20other%20lyricists%20apart%20from%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20first%20met%20him%20a%20week%20ago%2C%20and%20I%20visited%20his%20house%20to%20touch%20his%20feet%20in%20order%20to%20receive%20his%20blessing.%20He%20requested%20that%20I%20sing%20a%20song%20about%20Radha%20Krishna%2C%20which%20bestowed%20blessings%20upon%20me%2C%20and%20urged%20me%20to%20start%20over%20and%20succeed%20in%20my%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20Anand%20Raaj%20Anand%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArriving%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201964%20Kohli%20began%20looking%20for%20film%20work.%20With%20the%20release%20of%20the%20movie%20%3Ci%3EGunda%3C%2Fi%3E%20in%201969%2C%20he%20debuted%20in%20the%20Bollywood%20industry.%20His%20first%20big%20break%20came%20with%20the%20song%20%3Ci%3EGeet%20Gaata%20Hoon%20Main%3C%2Fi%3E%20from%20the%201971%20movie%20%3Ci%3ELaal%20Patthar%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20lyrics%20for%20several%20hit%20songs%20like%20%3Ci%3EAate%20Jaate%20Hanste%20Gaate%2C%20Kabootar%20Ja%20Ja%20Ja%2C%20Aaja%20Shaam%20Hone%20Aayee%2C%20Maine%20Pyar%20Kiya%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3EHum%20Aapke%20Hain%20Koun%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20Anu%20Malik%20formed%20a%20spectacular%20partnership%20in%20the%201990