lent%20contentions%20in%20the%20state%20during%20the%20period%20between%202016%20and%202019%20caused%20a%20further%20decline%20in%20the%20craft%20as%20the%20influx%20of%20tourists%20and%20their%20demands%20plunged.%20The%20final%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20tourism%20and%20exports%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20quoted%20by%20one%20of%20the%20exporters%20we%20interviewed%2C%20the%20annual%20turnover%20of%20the%20export%20line%20of%20Kashmir%20fell%20from%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%20to%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore%2C%20all%20due%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20pandemic-induced%20lockdowns.%20Such%20a%20large%20fall%20in%20exports%20further%20deteriorated%20the%20market%20conditions%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20the%20art%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20impact%20of%20commercialisation%20on%20the%20paper%20mache%20industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20hardly%20any%20help%20from%20the%20government%2C%20the%20artisans%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20depend%20on%20bulk%20export%20orders%20to%20support%20their%20livelihood%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20they%20are%20hardly%20able%20to%20manage%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20Saad%20Naqash*%2C%2037%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CChanges%20in%20the%20craft%20of%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20have%20been%20significant%2C%20driven%20by%20consumer%20demands.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20traditional%20design%20of%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20has%20undergone%20a%20complete%20transformation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25165438%2Fimage-1247.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22755%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire