s%20the%20artisans%20who%20must%20face%20the%20music%20and%20endure%20the%20difference%2C%20resulting%20in%20less%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fvx8Ypz8rif8%3Fsi%3DGRRLUy3ltEKjXTn5%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuqsood%20Ahmad%20Ganie%20sheds%20more%20light%20on%20this%20situation%20by%20comparing%20the%20costs%20of%20raw%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20balls%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20makers%20of%20raw%20material%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20bargain%20for%20a%20better%20price%20because%20only%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20individuals%20are%20now%20available%20who%20can%20make%20bases%20of%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20products.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20raw%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20balls%20for%20%3Cem%3Echith%20wala%3C%2Fem%3E%20(made%20of%20raw%20material)%20belonging%20to%20the%20Sunni%20community%20has%20increased%20from%20Rs%208%20to%20Rs%2019%20from%202019%20to%202023%20but%20the%20cost%20for%20us%20who%20give%20the%20final%20touch%20to%20these%20products%20has%20decreased.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArtists%20like%20us%20are%20not%20getting%20their%20due%20recognition%20and%20amount.%20Another%20example%20here%2C%20last%20year%20the%20labour%20cost%20per%20box%20was%20Rs%2015%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20camel%20colour%20tubes%20was%20Rs%206%2C%20but%20now%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20same%20colour%20is%20Rs%2030%20and%20the%20labour%20cost%20of%20the%20box%20is%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExporters%20believe%20that%20while%20government%20officials%20claim%20to%20have%20helped%20the%20overworked%20artisans%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20quite%20the%20opposite.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20small%20artisans%20find%20no%20relaxation%20in%20taxes%2C%20namely%20GST.%20They%20have%20to%20pay%20extra%20money%20for%20the%20raw%20materials%2C%20which%20further%20drives%20up%20the%20cost%20price%20while%20they%20receive%20no%20return%20on%20the%20taxes%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20GST%20number.%20Even%20with%20higher%20expenses%2C%20the%20selling%20price%20for%20the%20products%20remains%20the%20same%2C%20leaving%20less%20profit%20margin%20for%20both%20the%20artisans%20and%20the%20exporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20side%2C%20the%20exporters%20face%20difficulties%20due%20to%20inconsistent%20transport%20charges%20and%20stoppage%20at%20customs%20%E2%80%93%20both%20of%20which%20can%20easily%20be%20solved%20by%20government%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20larger%20area%20of%20concern%20is%20the%20disparity%20between%20the%20earnings%20of%20the%20artisans%20and%20those%20of%20exporters.%20Not%20only%20do%20the%20artisans%20believe%20that%20exporters%20give%20them%20low%20wages%20for%20the%20products%2C%20but%20they%20also%20give%20this%20minimal%20wage%20in%20instalments%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20the%20artisans%20to%20survive.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20no%20intervention%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20end%20to%20aid%20the%20underpaid%20artisans%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20a%20monopolistic%20situation%20has%20come%20up%20where%20artists%20remain%20with%20limited%20options%20for%20selling%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%3Cem%3ENames%20of%20all%20respondents%20have%20been%20changed%20to%20protect%20their%20identity%20and%20maintain%20anonymity.%20The%20authors%20would%20like%20to%20especially%20thank%20Rekha%20Pachauri%20and%20Meera%20Shirodkar%20for%20their%20assistance%20with%20fieldwork%2C%20interviews%20and%20the%20audio-video%20documentation%20of%20the%20study.%20Without%20their%20support%2C%20this%20study%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible.%20All%20photographs%20are%20credited%20to%20them%20and%20Ishfaq%20Ahmad%20Wani.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%20and%20Humanities%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20Ishfaq%20Ahmad%20Wani%20is%20a%20Contributing%20Research%20Analyst%20with%20CNES%20Visual%20Storyboards.%20Tavleen%20Kaur%20and%20Hima%20Trisha%20are%20Senior%20Research%20Analysts%20and%20CNES%20Visual%20Storyboards%20team%20leads.%20Yashovardhan%20Chaturvedi%20and%20Anousha%20Singh%20are%20Research%20Analysts%20with%20CNES.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693035007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25164826%2Fimage-1246.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkashmir-papier-mache-craft-wane-authenticity%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20traditional%20papier-m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20pieces%20of%20art%20from%20Kashmir%20are%20well-known%20worldwide.%20Owing%20to%20years%20of%20natural%20catastrophes%2C%20violent%20conflicts%2C%20and%20a%20pandemic%2C%20the%20tradition%20is%20struggling%20to%20stay%20afloat%20in%20a%20world%20of%20westernised%20demands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkashmir-papier-mache-craft-wane-authenticity%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sham%20Kaushal%20Deconstructs%20Sunny%20Deol's%20Viral%20Gadar%202%20Hand%20Pump%20Scene%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESunny%20Deol%20and%20Ameesha%20Patel's%C2%A0%3Ci%3EGadar%202%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0has%20taken%20the%20country%20by%20storm.%20The%20sequel%20of%C2%A0%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fgadar-composer-uttam-singh-slams-makers-for-not-talking-to-him-before-using-his-songs-in-sequel-4328353%5C%22%3EGadar%3A%20Ek%20Prem%20Katha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Econtinues%20to%20roar%20at%20the%20box%20office%20and%20how.%20After%20all%2C%C2%A0%3Ci%3EGadar%202%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eis%20eyeing%20to%20enter%20the%20500-crore%20club.%20From%20the%20songs%20to%20the%20action%20sequences%2C%20the%20film%20has%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20critics%20and%20fans%20alike.%20Now%2C%20action%20director%20Sham%20Kaushal%20has%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20fan-favourite%20hand%20pump%20scene%20in%20the%20film.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmovies%2Fbollywood%2Fvideo%2Faction-director-sham-kaushal-talks-about-his-journey-success-of-gadar-2-and-much-more-2424832-2023-08-22%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sham%20Kaushal%2C%20who%20is%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20and%20Sunny%20Kaushal's%20father%2C%20revealed%20that%20the%20hand%20pump%20for%20him%20was%20not%20just%20a%20prop%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20an%20even%20bigger%20hero%20than%20Sunny%20Deol.%E2%80%9D%20The%20veteran%20action%20director%20revealed%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20started%20on%20the%20page%2C%20with%20the%20writing%20and%20the%20direction.%20But%20executing%20it%20was%20my%20responsibility.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESham%20Kaushal%20added%20how%20even%20a%20minute%20change%20in%20the%20cinematography%20would%20have%20%E2%80%9Cruined%E2%80%9D%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20scene.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20a%20slight%20change%20to%20the%20closeups%20in%20that%20sequence%20would%20have%20ruined%20it.%20My%20take%20on%20it%20was%20that%20the%20hand%20pump%20wasn't%20a%20hand%20pump%2C%20but%20an%20even%20bigger%20hero%20than%20Sunny%20Deol%20had%20suddenly%20appeared%20off-screen%20behind%20him.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESham%20Kaushal%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20tactic%20to%20not%20reveal%20the%20hand%20pump%20in%20the%20first%20go%2C%20but%20to%20make%20it%20appear%20like%20a%20%E2%80%9Chulk%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn't%20immediately%20reveal%20who%20he%20%5BSunny%20Deol%5D%20had%20seen%20out%20of%20frame%2C%20but%20made%20it%20seem%20like%20an%20even%20bigger%20Hulk%20was%20standing%20there.%20Then%20we%20added%20reactions%2C%20and%20built%20tension%2C%20and%20only%20then%20did%20we%20reveal%20the%20hand%20pump.%20If%20we'd%20revealed%20the%20hand%20pump%20immediately%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20as%20fun%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sham%20Kaushal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20working%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsunny-deol-s-gadar-2-becomes-first-film-to-be-screened-at-new-parliament-building-4329606%5C%22%3ESunny%20Deol%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20action%20director%20said%20that%20personally%2C%20he%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccool%20guy%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20revealed%20they%20would%20always%20%E2%80%9Cgreet%20each%20other%20with%20a%C2%A0%3Ci%3EPunjabi%20jhappi%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20set.%20Sham%20Kaushal%20added%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20actor%20comes%20in%20front%20of%20the%20camera%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20like%20watching%20a%20lion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fgadar-2-box-office-collection-day-14-sunny-deols-blockbuster-wreaks-havoc-in-week-2-4327955%5C%22%3EGadar%202%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Ewas%20released%20on%20August%2011.%20The%20film%2C%20apart%20from%20Sunny%20Deol%20and%20Ameesha%20Patel%2C%20also%20stars%20Utkarsh%20Sharma%20and%20Simrat%20Kaur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693034400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fhhojl8n8_sunny-_625x300_26_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fgadar-2-action-director-sham-kaushal-has-this-to-say-about-the-iconic-hand-pump-scene-4331212%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sham%20Kaushal%20added%20how%20even%20a%20minute%20change%20in%20the%20cinematography%20would%20have%20%26quot%3Bruined%26quot%3B%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20scene.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainmen