20powers%20of%20state%20governments.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EL.K.%20Advani%20told%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20then%20Union%20government%2C%20through%20the%20Bill%2C%20was%20trying%20to%20directly%20influence%20the%20panchayats%20in%20states.%20Three%20decades%20later%2C%20the%20government%20to%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmargdarshak-mandal-yet-to-hold-its-first-meeting%2Farticle6802575.ece.%5C%22%3EAdvani%20has%20been%20a%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmargdarshak-mandal-yet-to-hold-its-first-meeting%2Farticle6802575.ece.%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emargdarshak%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20guide%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20indulging%20in%20worse%20federal%20intrusions.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20happening%20now%20is%20a%20multi-level%20operation%20designed%20to%20harass%20and%20tire%20out%20the%20opposition%20governments%20and%20thus%20make%20them%20unpopular.%20It%20is%20a%20calculated%20federal%20trespass%20aimed%20at%20simultaneously%20stretching%20the%20long%20arm%20of%20duopoly%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20interiors.%20Success%20of%20the%20Delhi%20model%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20so%20ruthlessly%20enforced%20to%20strangulate%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20and%20paralyse%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%93%20has%20emboldened%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20extend%20the%20experiment%20to%20other%20opposition-ruled%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20two%20years%2C%20the%20governors%20have%20been%20encouraged%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lg-directs-chief-secretary-to-recover-rs-97-crore-from-aap-for-political-advertisements%5C%22%3Ebehave%20like%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20V.K.%20Saxena%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fear%20of%20judicial%20spat