ender%20curriculum%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20be%20integrated%20into%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20education%20revolution%20in%20schools.%20The%20singular%20most%20important%20reason%20is%20that%20education%20should%20be%20inclusive%20and%20promote%20consciousness-raising%20among%20students%2C%20teachers%2C%20parents%20and%20policymakers%20for%20a%20more%20equal%20and%20violence-free%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGender%20is%20not%20only%20an%20unequal%20system%20of%20power%20relations%20but%20also%20a%20compelling%20marker%20of%20identity%20that%20intersects%20with%20other%20axes%20of%20inequalities%20like%20caste%20and%20class.%20So%20fundamental%20are%20the%20everyday%20negotiations%20on%20gender%20that%20an%20early%20school%20curriculum%20built%20around%20its%20complexities%20will%20only%20ease%20lived%20realities%20and%20confront%20injustices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20education%20is%20a%20practice%20of%20freedom%2C%20it%20must%20find%20its%20emancipatory%20worth%20in%20both%20responding%20classrooms%20and%20foundational%20curriculum.%20Both%20are%20interconnected%20to%20each%20other%20in%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20of%20strength%20and%20fragility.%20Progressive%20education%20must%20be%20a%20quest%20for%20self-actualisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStructural%20reform%20of%20equity-focused%20curricular%20decisions%20can%20no%20longer%20ignore%20the%20links%20between%20students%E2%80%99%20achievements%20and%20their%20diverse%20and%20unequal%20socio-economic%20backgrounds.%20Thus%2C%20a%20resilient%20education%20system%20has%20to%20foster%20a%20learning%20environment%20that%20enables%20affective%20skills%2C%20critical%20thinking%20and%20innovation.%20Herein%20lies%20the%20need%20for%20constructive%20engagement%20with%20the%20pedagogy%20of%20gender%20performance%20that%20will%20prepare%20children%20to%20be%20democratic%20citizens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPedagogy%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20constituent%20element%20of%20curricular%20development%20is%20pedagogy.%20It%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98complex%20philosophy%2C%20politics%20and%20practice%20of%20education%20that%20bears%20an%20ethical%20and%20political%20commitment%20to%20transforming%20oppressive%20social%20conditions.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20gendered%20pedagogy%20should%20essentially%20be%20%E2%80%98humanising%E2%80%99%20and%20build%20on%20the%20richness%20of%20a%20teacher-student%20relationship.%20Learning%20social%20responsibility%20and%20political%20agency%20are%20informed%20choices%20from%20such%20a%20philosophical%20standpoint.%20Locating%20learning%20in%20social%2Fgender%20issues%20and%20connecting%20with%20shared%20experiences%20and%20confessions%20in%20classroom%20spaces%20are%20fruitful%20takeaways%20for%20collective%20progress.%20Unless%20voices%20are%20unsilenced%2C%20shame%20will%20not%20allow%20children%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20being%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20street%20at%20night%20feels%20or%20how%20technology%20is%20misused%20for%20online%20harassment%20of%20girls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKnowledge%20production%20and%20its%20claims%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20central%20methodological%20question%20for%20curriculum%20development%20would%20be%20how%20and%20where%20would%20gender%20find%20a%20place.%20My%20answer%20would%20be%20everywhere%3A%20in%20textbook%20chapters%20and%20playrooms.%20Teaching%20is%20a%20performative%20act%20that%20has%20to%20be%20embedded%20in%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20plan-act-observe-reflect%20framework.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20question%20values%20and%20normative%20assumptions%20in%20disciplines%20that%20reinforce%20patterns%20of%20subordination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20unrecognised%20influence%20of%20gender%20on%20the%20production%20of%20dominant%20knowledge%20and%20existing%20knowledge%20claims%20needs%20nuanced%20classroom%20discussions.%20For%20example%2C%20exploring%20if%20there%20can%20be%20a%20naturally%20sexed%20body%20will%20enable%20an%20engagement%20with%20concerns%20of%20sexuality%2C%20problems%20of%20heteronormativity%2C%20consent%20and%20laws.%20In%20a%20science%20class%2C%20teachers%20could%20discuss%20gendered%20patterns%20in%20scientific%20imagery%20that%20may%20not%20be%20accurate.%20An%20example%20could%20be%20the%20use%20of%20gendered%20metaphors%20in%20human%20reproduction%20that%20presents%20the%20female%20body%20as%20passive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12130232%2FJagseer_S_Sidhu_teaching_school_students_about_Wikipedia.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12130232%2FJagseer_S_Sidhu_teaching_school_students_about_Wikipedia.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12130232%2FJagseer_S_Sidhu_teaching_school_students_about_Wikipedia-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-657642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22767%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20a%20school.%20Photo%3A%20Jagseer%20S%20Sidhu%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELanguage%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20we%20believe%20in%20John%20Locke%E2%80%99s%20words%20that%20the%20human%20mind%20begins%20as%20%E2%80%98a%20white%20paper%20void%20of%20all%20characters%20without%20any%20ideas%E2%80%99%20then%20the%20inner%20theatre%20of%20mind%20needs%20nurturing%20from%20childhood.%20Classroom%20practices%20that%20are%20uncritical%20of%20language%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20buttress%20gender%20stereotypes%20are%20problematic%20spaces%20of%20learning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESexism%20in%20language%20enhances%20male%20control%20over%20the%20production%20of%20cultural%20norms.%20Words%20for%20women%20are%20more%20sexualised%20than%20words%20for%20men.%20Often%2C%20women%20find%20themselves%20at%20a%20loss%20for%20words%20to%20articulate%20their%20existential%20problems%20like%20sexual%20harassment%20or%20menstruation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaleness%20in%20language%20constrains%20thought%20and%20even%20possibilities%20of%20an%20alternative%20vision%20of%20reality.%20Classroom%20pedagogical%20strategy%20can%20experiment%20with%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20language%20of%20their%20own.%20It%20could%20become%20a%20cautionary%20tale%20for%20the%20violence%20of%20language%20that%20normalises%20the%20use%20of%20cuss%20words%20in%20conversations%20among%20students.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAddressing%20the%20problem%20of%20masculinities%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20extraordinariness%20of%20a%20gender%20curriculum%20lies%20in%20questioning%20hegemonic%20masculinity%20too.%20Patriarchy%20adversely%20impacts%20not%20only%20women%20but%20also%20men.%20Marginalised%20men%20are%20often%20subject%20to%20oppressive%20power%20operated%20by%20other%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20classroom%20has%20to%20probe%20anxieties%20of%20%E2%80%98proving%E2%80%99%20one%E2%80%99s%20masculinity%20to%20blend%20solidarity%20between%20different%20genders.%20Interrogating%20ideas%20of%20heteronormative%20binaries%20could%20be%20a%20good%20beginning%20to%20naturalise%20sexually%20diverse%20identities.%20The%20association%20of%20aggression%20with%20masculine%20standards%20of%20success%2C%20power%20and%20vitality%20could%20be%20a%20moot%20point%20in%20understanding%20the%20dynamics%20of%20violence%20that%20plagues%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECognitive%20and%20moral%20development%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20curriculum%20has%20to%20do%20away%20with%20sexist%20standards%20of%20reason.%20Traditional%20learning%20tends%20to%20focus%20on%20curriculum%20as%20an%20object%20or%20textbook%20instead%20of%20an%20embodied%20world%20of%20children.%20New%20pedagogical%20techniques%20have%20to%20re-centre%20around%20feeling%2C%20empathy%20and%20passion.%20%E2%80%98Caring%E2%80%99%20in%20classrooms%20can%20propel%20more%20responses%20to%20conversations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20point%20is%20to%20create%20meaningful%20spaces%20for%20finding%20voices%20through%20coalescent%20argumentation%20that%20exposes%20gender%20stereotypes%20and%20intervenes%20in%20the%20institutional%20structures%20that%20sustain%20intersectional%20oppression.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20good%20example%20of%20such%20cognitive%20capacity%20building%20is%20through%20art%20education.%20Meanings%20to%20specific%20visual%20artworks%20can%20be%20discussed%20to%20allow%20students%20to%20think%20about%20how%20gender%20biases%20are%20inscribed%20to%20a%20work%20of%20art%20or%20even%20how%20students%20process%20an%20artwork%20from%20their%20gendered%20positionalities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20way%20forward%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20gender%20curriculum%20has%20to%20evolve%20for%20systemic%20change%20that%20infuses%20agency%20in%20teachers%20and%20students%20alike.%20By%20rendering%20visible%20gendered%20cultural%20inscriptions%2C%20it%20can%20benefit%20from%20dialogic%2C%20dialectically%20educative%20encounters%20in%20the%20classrooms.%20The%20transition%20from%20%E2%80%98the%20will%20to%20know%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98the%20will%20to%20become%E2%80%99%20must%20be%20a%20classroom%20habit.%20Agreeing%20with%20Judith%20Butler%2C%20the%20one-goal%20mission%20is%20%E2%80%98to%20think%20through%20the%20possibility%20of%20subverting%20and%20displacing%E2%80%99%20perversions%20of%20gendered%20ideas%20that%20interrupt%20the%20progress%20of%20any%20citizen.%20Transformative%20change%20in%20the%20attitudes%20of%20children%20will%20be%20the%20first%20step%20to%20revolutionise%20society.%20Delhi%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20shy%20away%20from%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnita%20Tagore%20is%20associate%20professor%20at%20Kalindi%20College%2C%20University%20of%20Delhi.%20She%20is%20a%20lawyer%20and%20socio-legal%20researcher.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693029653000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fgendering-the-education-revolution-in-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unrecognised%20influence%20of%20gender%20in%20knowledge%20production%20needs%20nuanced%20classroom%20discussions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fgendering-the-education-revolution-in-delhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20imposes%2020%25%20export%20duty%20on%20parboiled%20rice%3B%20MEP%20on%20basmati%20rice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693029646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F10%2Ffull%2F1691637086-051.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcentre-imposes-20-export-duty-on-parboiled-rice-mep-on-basmati-rice-123082600238_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Basmati%20MEP%20will%20end%20once%20parboiled%20levy%20kicks%20in%20on%20Oct%2016%3B%20Basmati%20MEP%20will%20be%20reviewed%20in%20Oct%20first%20week%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcentre-imposes-20-export-duty-on-parboiled-ric