2%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20airport%20runs%20out%20of%20parking%20spots%20for%20planes%20for%20the%20G20%20summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693028580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-03%2F20%2Ffull%2F1679288641-6746.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-airport-runs-out-of-parking-spots-for-planes-for-the-g20-summit-123082600246_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20govt%20has%20directed%20airlines%20to%20cut%20a%20quarter%20of%20their%20flight%20frequency%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Delhi.%201000%20flights%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20affected%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-airport-runs-out-of-parking-spots-for-planes-for-the-g20-summit-123082600246_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-airport-runs-out-of-parking-spots-for-planes-for-the-g20-summit-123082600246_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-airport-runs-out-of-parking-spots-for-planes-for-the-g20-summit-123082600246_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Violence%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Says%20Trial%20in%20CBI%20Cases%20Will%20Be%20Conducted%20in%20Assam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%2C%20August%2025%2C%20said%20that%20the%20trial%20of%20criminal%20cases%20connected%20with%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20is%20probing%20can%20be%20conducted%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fmanipur-violence-supreme-court-trial-cbi-cases-assam-statements-virtually%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said%20victims%20should%20not%20be%20expected%20to%20travel%20to%20Assam%20and%20should%20instead%20be%20facilitated%20to%20provide%20statements%20through%20video%20conferences.%20The%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20was%20assured%20by%20solicitor%20general%20(SG)%20Tushar%20Mehta%20that%20proper%20internet%20facilities%20shall%20be%20provided%20in%20Manipur%20to%20allow%20statements%20via%20a%20video%20conference.%20However%2C%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20travel%20to%20Guwahati%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20physically%20can%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20you%20want%20the%20statements%20to%20be%20recorded%20in%20Manipur%20and%20not%20in%20Assam%20or%20wherever%20the%20victims%20are%20%E2%80%A6%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20will%20take%20care%20and%20the%20entire%20process%20will%20be%20done%20virtually%20%E2%80%A6%20We%20will%20not%20ask%20the%20survivor%20to%20travel%20to%20Assam..%20and%20we%20will%20have%20statements%20and%20evidence%20recorded%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20observed%20orally%20in%20response%20to%20concerns%20raised%20by%20lawyers%20Colin%20Gonsalves%20and%20Vrinda%20Grover%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Senior%20Advocate%20Indira%20Jaising%E2%80%99s%20query%20over%20why%20Assam%20has%20been%20chosen%20for%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20trial%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESG%20Mehta%20said%20that%20Assam%20was%20chosen%20because%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cmaximum%E2%80%9D%20internet%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20passed%20some%20directions%20to%20ensure%20a%20fair%20process.%20Among%20these%20was%20asking%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20to%20nominate%20%E2%80%9Cone%20or%20more%20officers%20above%20the%20rank%20of%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20First%20Class%20and%20sessions%20judge%20to%20deal%20with%20such%20trial%20cases%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20judicial%20custody%20shall%20be%20permitted%20in%20Manipur%2C%20while%20the%20recording%20of%20statements%20under%20Section%20164%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%20shall%20be%20recorded%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20local%20magistrate%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20acting%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20shall%20designate%20one%20or%20more%20magistrates%20for%20this%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20applications%20for%20the%20production%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20remand%2C%20judicial%20custody%2C%20extension%20of%20custody%2C%20and%20other%20proceedings%20are%20allowed%20to%20be%20conducted%20online%2C%20bearing%20in%20mind%20both%20distance%20and%20security%20issues%20at%20the%20courts%20that%20will%20be%20designated%20to%20conduct%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20said%20that%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20shall%20nominate%20judges%20who%20are%20conversant%20with%20one%20or%20more%20languages%20spoken%20in%20Manipur%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20criminal%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20directions%20came%20during%20a%20hearing%20of%20a%20batch%20of%20pleas%20related%20to%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20in%20Manipur.%20Among%20the%20petitioners%20were%20two%20Kuki%20women%20whose%20assault%20by%20a%20mob%20was%20recorded%20on%20video%20and%20later%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20video%20emerged%2C%20the%20top%20court%20took%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20constituted%20an%20all-women%20committee%20%E2%80%93%20headed%20by%20the%20former%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20high%20court%20Gita%20Mittal%20%E2%80%93%20to%20suggest%20measures.%20It%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-supreme-court-gita-mittal-committee-report-documents-compensation%5C%22%3Efiled%20three%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20findings%20on%20the%20violence%2C%20suggesting%20recovery%20and%20reconstruction%20of%20documents%20lost%20in%20arson%20and%20gunfire%20and%20just%20compensation%20rules%20and%20the%20appointment%20of%20domain%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEthnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20have%20been%20ongoing%20since%20May%203.%20More%20than%20150%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20several%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced.%20Leaders%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20say%20they%20have%20no%20faith%20in%20the%20government%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20a%20Meitei%2C%20and%20that%20a%20separate%20administration%20for%20the%20Kuki%20tribe%20is%20the%20only%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693027742000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-violence-cbi-cases-trial-assam-supreme-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20court%20said%20victims%20should%20not%20be%20expected%20to%20travel%20to%20Assam%20and%20should%20instead%20be%20facilitated%20to%20provide%20statements%20through%20video%20conferences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-violence-cbi-cases-trial-assam-supreme-court%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SEBI%20Says%20Probe%20Into%20Adani%20Group%20Nearly%20Complete%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F09152137%2Fsebi-pti-1129909-1658745014-1185298-1674839765.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20market%20regulator%20SEBI%20has%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20nearly%E2%80%9D%20completed%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20possible%20violations%20of%20securities%20law%2C%20it%20said%20in%20a%20filing%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-market-regulator-tells-top-court-it-has-completed-adani-probe-2023-08-25%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%20said%20it%20has%20been%20investigating%2024%20transactions%20involving%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20listed%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20which%20lost%20more%20than%20%24100%20billion%20in%20market%20capitalisation%20this%20year%20after%20the%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20accused%20it%20of%20stock%20manipulation%20and%20accounting%20fraud.%20Of%20these%2C%20the%20findings%20in%2022%20have%20been%20finalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%20said%20in%20the%20court%20filing%20that%20it%20is%20prepared%20to%20take%20any%20action%20if%20the%20findings%20so%20require.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2024%20transactions%2C%2013%20Adani%20Group%20dealings%20were%20investigated%20for%20possible%20violations%20of%20related-party%20transaction%20rules.%20The%20market%20regulator%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20on%20some%20offshore%20deals%20covered%2012%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20portfolio%20investors%20who%20were%20public%20shareholders%20of%20Adani%20group%20companies%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20some%20entities%20related%20to%20these%20investors%20are%20located%20in%20tax%20haven%20jurisdictions%2C%20%E2%80%9Cestablishing%20the%20economic%20interest%20shareholders%20of%20the%2012%20FPIs%20remains%20a%20challenge%E2%80%9D%2C%20SEBI%20said.%20It%20has%20sought%20information%20from%20five%20foreign%20countries%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20the%20filing%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fsebi-submits-adani-report-to-supreme-court-says-probe-completed%2Farticleshow%2F103076118.cms%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20SEBI%20also%20probed%20two%20cases%20on%20stock%20price%20manipulation%20and%20one%20each%20on%20minimum%20public%20holding%20norms%2C%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%2C%20the%20takeover%20code%20and%20trading%20before%20and%20after%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20was%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20scope%20of%20the%20investigation%20on%20related-party%20transactions%20was%20to%20ascertain%20allegations%20relating%20to%20possible%20material%20misrepresentation%20in%20financial%20statements%2C%20misstatements%2C%20attempts%20to%20circumvent%20regulations%20and%20fraudulent%20transactions%2C%20if%20any%2C%20under%20various%20SEBI%20rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20filing%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulator%20said%20it%20carried%20out%20a%20%E2%80%9Cholistic%20analysis%E2%80%9D%20in%20relation%20to%20alleged%20price%20volume%20manipulation%20in%20seven%20Adani%20Group%20stocks.%20it%20also%C2%A0examined%20%E2%80%9Cwhether%20the%20short%20positions%20taken%20by%20certain%20entities%20in%20Adani%20Group%20companies%20were%20unusual%20around%20the%20time%20the%20report%20was%20released%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20into%20the%20Adani%20Group%20began%20after%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%20The%20regulator%20will%20submit%20its%20findings%20to%20a%20six-member%20panel%2C%20also%20constituted%20by%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693025549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F09152137%2Fsebi-pti-1129909-1658745014-1185298-1674839765.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsebi-says-probe-into-adani-group-