athed%20his%20last%20the%20same%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20findings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20surrender%2C%20they%20did%20not%20want%20themselves%20to%20be%20found%20by%20the%20Americans%20or%20the%20British%2C%20shielding%20Netaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Netaji%20was%20found%20to%20re-emerge%20from%20India%20or%20from%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Communists%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fjapan-netaji-death-files%5C%22%3Ebonafide%20of%20post-war%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20towards%20the%20British%20and%20the%20Americans%20would%20be%20at%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%2C%20therefore%2C%20scuttled%20Netaji%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20fly%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20they%20tricked%20Netaji%20by%20not%20returning%20him%20to%20Indian%20soil.%20They%20diverted%20his%20plane%20towards%20Saigon%20on%20the%20plea%20that%20they%20could%20avoid%20the%20aerial%20vigilance%20of%20the%20Allied%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20they%20separated%20five%20of%20his%20six%20companions%20at%20Saigon%20and%20told%20him%20that%20he%20would%20be%20taken%20to%20Tokyo%20despite%20his%20strong%20rejection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20thorough%20investigation%2C%20the%20IIL%E2%80%99s%20finding%20was%20that%20the%20plane%20crash%20was%20deliberate.%20It%20was%20a%20manipulated%20%E2%80%98crash%E2%80%99.%20The%20intention%20was%20not%20to%20kill.%20But%20to%20spoil%20Netaji%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20meet%20the%20Communists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25164434%2Fbose-15.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25164434%2Fbose-15.jpg%20910w%2C%20https%3A%2F%