k.%20This%20helped%20me%20develop%20vocabulary%2C%20fluency%20and%20confidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20out%20with%201%2C000%20followers%20in%202018%2C%20her%20Instagram%20page%20has%20over%2070%2C000%20followers%20today.%20She%20also%20has%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20and%20Discord%20server%20to%20teach%20the%20language.%20Her%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20learning%20Malayalam%20fun%2C%20accessible%20and%20easy%20while%20catering%20to%20the%20many%20Malayalis%20who%20are%20living%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20Malayalis%20who%20live%20abroad%20and%20most%20of%20the%20younger%20generation%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20language%20well.%20There%20is%20a%20pride%20that%20people%20associate%20with%20speaking%20English%2C%20which%20unfortunately%20results%20in%20the%20mother%20tongue%20getting%20sidelined.%20My%20page%20is%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20people%20to%20ask%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20Malayalam%20die%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FNMlMdjgE5uk%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnglish%20medium%20education%20is%20becoming%20more%20popular%20in%20India%2C%20causing%20a%20decline%20in%