0mud%20walls%20were%20starting%20to%20chip%20away.%20When%20we%20saw%20it%20after%20all%20these%20years%2C%20we%20could%20tell%20it%20had%20seen%20much%20damage%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Susmitha.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tough%20call%20awaited%20the%20couple.%20Should%20they%20restore%20the%20home%2C%20furnish%20it%20or%20leave%20it%20as%20is%3F%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284474%2Fhow-couple-quit-city-life-to-build-sustainable-homestay-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esentimental%20value%20of%20the%20home%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecompelled%20them%20to%20choose%20the%20first%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%E2%80%99re%20so%20glad%20we%20did%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20simple%20idea%20taking%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20restore%20the%20place%2C%20they%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20thought%20of%20converting%20it%20into%20a%20homestay.%20The%20inspiration%20came%20after%20Susmitha%20read%20an%20article%20in%202000%20about%20the%20emergence%20of%20%E2%80%98homestay%20culture%E2%80%99%20in%20Coorg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20why%20not%20Chikmagalur%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20thought.%20The%20city%20boasted%20of%20forests%2C%20waterfalls%2C%20and%20beautiful%20grasslands%2C%20all%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20luscious%20Western%20Ghats.%20The%20couple%20wanted%20the%20city%20to%20be%20known%20on%20the%20world-map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20heritage%20home%20offers%20bird%20watching%2C%20trekking%2C%20hiking%2C%20cycling%20and%20more%20